Name: Blue-eyes White Dragon
Description:
An extremely rare   
card with
unsurpassed attack
and defense power.

Name: Mystical Elf
Description:
A delicate elf that 
lacks in offense
but has a terrific
defense backed by
mystical power.

Name: Hitotsu-me Giant
Description:
A one-eyed behemoth 
with thick, powerful
arms made for
delivering punishing
blows.

Name: Baby Dragon
Description:
Much more than just 
a child, this dragon
is gifted with
untapped power.

Name: Ryu-kishin
Description:
A very elusive 
creature that looks 
like a harmless
statue until it
attacks.

Name: Feral Imp
Description:
A playful little 
imp that lurks in 
the dark, waiting to
attack an unwary
enemy.

Name: Winged Dragon #1
Description:
A dragon commonly 
found guarding 
mountain fortresses.
Its signature attack
is a sweeping dive 
from out of the blue.

Name: Mushroom Man
Description:
Found in moist
areas, this monster 
launches poison
spores against its
enemies.

Name: Shadow Specter
Description:
Ghostly beast that 
appears in the
wasteland and is
particularly
troublesome when
faced in large
numbers.

Name: Blackland Fire Dragon
Description:
A dragon that dwells
in the depths of
darkness. Its
defensive capability
suffers from its
poor eyesight.

Name: Sword Arm of Dragon
Description:
With a body covered 
in sword-like
thorns, nothing
dares stand in the
way of this monster 
when it charges.

Name: Swamp Battleguard
Description:
This creature is    
armed with a spiked 
club that can
destroy almost
anything in its path.
Rumored to have a
brother that is just
as destructive.

Name: Tyhone
Description:
Capable of firing
cannonballs from its
mouth for long-range
attacks against
enemies.

Name: Battle Steer
Description:
A bull monster often
found in the woods.
Charges enemy
monsters with a pair
of razor-sharp horns.

Name: Flame Swordsman
Description:
A fighter gifted
with the power of
fire.
Attacks enemies with
a sword that
launches flames.

Name: Time Wizard
Description:
A sorcerer capable
of bending time to
his will. Though not
powerful at first
glance, appearances 
can be deceiving.

Name: Right Leg of the Forbidden One
Description:
A forbidden limb
sealed by magic.
Whoever breaks
this seal will know
infinite power.
Only one card of
this type may be
included in a deck.

Name: Left Leg of the Forbidden One
Description:
A forbidden limb
sealed by magic.
Whoever breaks
this seal will know
infinite power.
Only one card of
this type may be
included in a deck.

Name: Right Arm of the Forbidden One
Description:
A forbidden limb
sealed by magic.
Whoever breaks
this seal will know
infinite power.
Only one card of
this type may be
included in a deck.

Name: Left Arm of the Forbidden One
Description:
A forbidden limb
sealed by magic.
Whoever breaks
this seal will know
infinite power.
Only one card of
this type may be
included in a deck.

Name: Exodia the Forbidden
Description:
Once combined with
arms and legs, this 
monster is freed
from its magical
chains.
Only one card of
this type may be
included in a deck.

Name: Summoned Skull
Description:
An entity with dark
powers for confusing
the enemy. Among the
FIEND class of
monsters, this is a 
pretty rare card.

Name: The Wicked Worm Beast
Description:
A monster worm
created by the
powers of darkness. 
It suddenly appears 
from under the
ground to attack its
enemies.

Name: Skull Servant
Description:
A skeletal ghost
that isn't strong
but can mean trouble
in large numbers.

Name: Horn Imp
Description:
A small imp that
dwells in the dark.
Its single horn
makes it a
formidable opponent.

Name: Battle Ox
Description:
A monster with
tremendous power.
Destroys enemies
with a swing of its
axe.

Name: Beaver Warrior
Description:
What this creature 
lacks in size,
it makes up for
in defense when
battling in the
meadow.

Name: Rock Ogre Grotto #1
Description:
Protected by a solid
body of rock, this
creature throws
a bone-shattering
punch.

Name: Mountain Warrior
Description:
A solid warrior that
can move swiftly
over rough terrain.

Name: Zombie Warrior
Description:
A deceptively
fragile-looking
skeleton warrior
that is known for
its swift and
precise attacks.

Name: Koumori Dragon
Description:
A vicious,
fire-breathing
dragon whose wicked
flames corrupt the
souls of its victims.

Name: Two-headed King Rex
Description:
An unusual and
rarely seen
two-headed dragon.

Name: Judge Man
Description:
For this
club-wielding
warrior, there is
no other outcome
to battle than
victory or defeat.

Name: Saggi the Dark Clown
Description:
This clown appears 
out of nowhere and 
executes some very 
strange moves to 
avoid enemy attacks.

Name: Dark Magician
Description:
The ultimate wizard 
in terms of attack
and defense.

Name: The Snake Hair
Description:
A monster with the
head of a poisonus
snake. One look will
turn an unwary
opponent to stone.

Name: Gaia the Dragon Champion
Description:
A warrior's prowess 
combines with a
dragon's speed to
create a powerful
offensive force.

Name: Gaia the Fierce Knight
Description:
A knight mounted on 
a horse that travels
faster than the wind.
His battle charge is
a force to be
reckoned with.

Name: Curse of Dragon
Description:
A wicked dragon that
taps dark forces to 
execute a powerful
attack.

Name: Dragon Piper
Description:
A jar carved with
strange patterns. It
has a particularly
high defense factor.

Name: Celtic Guardian
Description:
An elf, who learned
to wield a sword,
baffles enemies with
lightning-swift
attacks.

Name: Illusionist Faceless Mage
Description:
Manipulates enemy
attacks with the
power of illusion.
A very rare card.

Name: Karbonala Warrior
Description:
A very
average-looking
fighter with an
unusually high
attack factor.

Name: Rogue Doll
Description:
A unique doll gifted
with mystical power.
Particularly
powerful when
attacking against
dark forces.

Name: Oscillo Hero #2
Description:
Attacks its enemies
with thunder.

Name: Griffore
Description:
This creature's
tough hide deflects
just about any
attack.

Name: Torike
Description:
Not as tough as it
looks in terms of
defense.
This monster's
sharp horn gives it
an edge
when attacking.

Name: Sangan
Description:
A compact,
three-eyed monster
that is dangerous
when faced
in the dark.

Name: Big Insect
Description:
A giant ant that
dwells in the jungle.
Powerful in terms of
both ATK and DEF
factors.

Name: Basic Insect
Description:
Usually found
travelling in swarms,
this creature's
ideal environment is
the forest.

Name: Armored Lizard
Description:
A lizard with a very
tough hide and a
very vicious bite.

Name: Hercules Beetle
Description:
A massive beetle
with a tough hide
and a dangerous horn.

Name: Killer Needle
Description:
A huge bee with
exceptional strength.
Particularly
dangerous when a
swarm is encountered.

Name: Gokibore
Description:
A large, spherical
roach that attacks
its enemies by
rolling over them.
Its tough defense
makes it 
a formidable foe.

Name: Giant Flea
Description:
A giant
blood-sucking flea
that's devastating
when attacking.

Name: Larvae Moth
Description:
Not much in its
larval form,
this creature is a
force to be reckoned
with when it grows
to become a colossal
moth.

Name: Great Moth
Description:
A powerful creature
of the forest, this
huge moth attacks
its enemies by
spreading poison
dust with its wings.

Name: Kuriboh
Description:
By itself, this
small creature may
not seem like much.
But in the dark, it
attacks in numbers
as a formidable
force.

Name: Mammoth Graveyard
Description:
A mammoth that
protects the
gravesite of its
pack. It's
absolutely merciless
when facing
graverobbers.

Name: Great White
Description:
A giant white shark
with razor-sharp
teeth.

Name: Wolf
Description:
A rarely seen wolf
with a powerful nose
for catching the
scent of an enemy.

Name: Harpie Lady
Description:
A human-shaped
animal with wings.
Beautiful to watch,
but lethal when
engaged in battle.

Name: Harpie Lady Sisters
Description:
Three fierce sisters
who relentlessly
attack as a team.

Name: Tiger Axe
Description:
A fast and powerful
axe-wielding
beast warrior.

Name: Silver Fang
Description:
A snow wolf that's
beautiful to the eye
but absolutely
vicious in battle.

Name: Kojikocy
Description:
A man-hunter with
powerful arms that
can crush boulders.

Name: Perfectly Ultimate Great Moth
Description:
The final
incarnation of the
ultimate insect,
the Great Moth!

Name: Garoozis
Description:
An axe-swinging
beast warrior with
the head of
a dragon.

Name: Thousand Dragon
Description:
A dragon that has
grown and developed
over a thousand
years.

Name: Fiend Kraken
Description:
A massive squid that
suddenly appears
from the depths of
the sea to attack
unwary enemies.

Name: Jellyfish
Description:
An almost invisible,
semi-transparent
jellyfish that
drifts in the sea.

Name: Cocoon of Evolution
Description:
This creature is
capable of instantly
evolving larvae
into adults.

Name: Kairyu-shin
Description:
A sea dragon that's
referred to as the
"King of the Ocean".
It attacks its
enemies with huge
tidal waves.

Name: Giant Soldier of Stone
Description:
A giant warrior made
of stone. A punch
from this creature
has earth-shaking
results.

Name: Man-eating Plant
Description:
A meat-eating plant
that is attractive
to the eye but
dangerous when
approached.

Name: Krokodilus
Description:
A vicious crocodile
with intelligence.
Hard scales form
a natural armor
for this creature.

Name: Grappler
Description:
A devious snake with
a thick body that
wraps around an
enemy monster and
squeezes the life
out of it.

Name: Axe Raider
Description:
An axe-wielding
monster of
tremendous strength
and agility.

Name: Megazowler
Description:
Nothing stands in
the way of this
spike-covered
dinosaur.

Name: Uraby
Description:
Fast on its feet,
this dinosaur rips
enemies to shreds
with its sharp claws.

Name: Crawling Dragon #2
Description:
A powerful dragon
with teeth that can
grind almost
anything to dust.

Name: Red-eyes B. Dragon
Description:
A very rare card
with a high-level
ATK factor.

Name: Castle of Dark Illusions
Description:
A creature that can
generate darkness to
envelop all that
exists around it.

Name: Reaper of the Cards
Description:
This monster boasts
a strong defense and
a massive scythe
that cuts through
almost anything.

Name: King of Yamimakai
Description:
Wields the power of
darkness to destroy
its enemies.

Name: Barox
Description:
This creature flies
through the dark,
attacking its
enemies with its
long, hairy arms.

Name: Dark Chimera
Description:
A fire-breathing
monster that dwells
in the netherworld.

Name: Metal Guardian
Description:
A fiend guarding
the treasures of
the netherworld.
Its defense is
particularly high in
 a dark environment.

Name: Catapult Turtle
Description:
Well-protected by
its shell, this
monster flings
projectiles from
its catapult.

Name: Gyakutenno Megami
Description:
Uses her mystical
power to protect the
weak and provide
spiritual support.

Name: Mystic Horseman
Description:
Half man and half
horse, this monster
is known for its
extreme speed.

Name: Rabid Horseman
Description:
A powerful
and unstoppable
combination of
bull and horse.

Name: Zanki
Description:
Prefers to face
enemies one-on-one.
His swiftly drawn
blade delivers a
quick and immediate
finnish.

Name: Crawling Dragon
Description:
A weakened dragon
that can no longer
fly, but is still a
formidable force
to be reckoned with.

Name: Crass Clown
Description:
A performer
in the Dark Circus,
this clown drains
the strength of
its enemies with
strange dances.

Name: Armored Zombie
Description:
A warrior raised
from the beyond.
Blindly swings
a sharp blade with
devastating force.

Name: Dragon Zombie
Description:
A dragon revived by
sorcery. Its breath
is highly corrosive.

Name: Clown Zombie
Description:
A clown revived by
the powers of
darkness.
Its strange dance
has sent many 
monsters to their
ends.

Name: Pumpking the King of Ghosts
Description:
This pumpkin king
strikes at its
enemies with its
long tentacles.

Name: Battle Warrior
Description:
A warrior that
fights with his
bare hands.

Name: Wings of Wicked Flame
Description:
Soaring over
its enemies on wings
of crimson fire,
this monster attacks
by blasting flames
from its body.

Name: Mask of Darkness
Description:
A shadow mask
created by the hands
of a dark mage.

Name: Job-change Mirror
Description:
An indestructible,
wicked mirror that
blocks enemy attacks.

Name: Curtain of the Dark Ones
Description:
A curtain woven by
the hands of a
sorcerer. It is said
to enhance the power
of magic- users.

Name: Tomozaurus
Description:
A deceivingly small
creature that is so
vicious it attacks
both friend and foe
without discretion.

Name: Spirit of the Winds
Description:
A spirit of the wind
that freely sails
the skies. Known to
generate storms when
it's in a bad mood.

Name: Kageningen
Description:
Uses both its
physical and shadow
forms to attack,
making it
a difficult creature
to overcome.

Name: Graveyard and the Hand of Invitation
Description:
A final resting
place that enhances
the power of the
doomed and drains
that of the living.

Name: Goddess with the Third Eye
Description:
A goddess with an
all-seeing eye that
reveals all.

Name: Hero of the East
Description:
A samurai from the
Far East armed with
a razor-sharp sword.

Name: Doma The Angel of Silence
Description:
This angel rules
over the doomed
and administers it
when necessary.

Name: That Which Feeds on Life
Description:
A vile monster that
fuels its power by
draining the essence
of life from
its opponents.

Name: Dark Gray
Description:
Entirely gray,
this beast has
rarely been seen
by mortal eyes.

Name: White Magical Hat
Description:
A gentleman thief
that eludes the law
despite the fact
that he sticks out
like a sore thumb
with his silk hat
and white cape.

Name: Kamion Wizard
Description:
A magic-user that
controls chaos
and wields
a mighty sickle.

Name: Nightmare Scorpion
Description:
A very toxic
creature that
induces nightmares
and attacks its
victims with four
poison- tipped
stingers.

Name: Spirit of the Books
Description:
A spirit of the
books with infinite
knowledge and
an endless variety
of attack strategies.

Name: Supporter in the Shadows
Description:
A cute elf that
assists against
enemies while
remaining hidden
from sight.

Name: Trial of Nightmares
Description:
Passes judgment on
enemies that are
locked in coffins.

Name: Dream Clown
Description:
The mysterious dance
of this creature
draws its enemies
into eternal slumber.

Name: Sleeping Lion
Description:
Frequently
found sleeping,
this monster is
very dangerous
when awakened.

Name: Yamatano Dragon Scroll
Description:
This dragon is
conjured from
a picture scroll
to attack enemies.
It has a pretty
low defense factor.

Name: Dark Plant
Description:
A vicious flower
raised from polluted
soil and fertilized
by dark forces.

Name: Ancient Tool
Description:
An engine
of destruction
discovered in the
ruins of an ancient
civilization.

Name: Faith Bird
Description:
A bird with a very
long tail that
attacks with a light
that emanates from
its entire being.

Name: Orion the Battle King
Description:
A mysterious
creature known as
the king of warriors,
but nobody has lived
long enough to tell
how it earned
its reputation.

Name: Ansatsu
Description:
A silent and swift
warrior specializing
in sneak attack.

Name: LaMoon
Description:
A sorcerer who lives
on the moon and
attacks opponents
with the power
of lunar light.

Name: Nemuriko
Description:
A child-like
creature that
controls a sleep
spirit to beckon
enemies into eternal
slumber.

Name: Weather Control
Description:
This monster is
capable of
manipulating the
weather. This power
is the reason behind
the changing climate
of mountains.

Name: Octoberser
Description:
A strange creature
with the head
of a fish and
the tentacles of
an octopus that
attacks its enemies
with spears.

Name: The 13th Grave
Description:
A zombie that
suddenly appeared
from plot
#13 - supposedly
an empty grave.

Name: Charubin the Fire Knight
Description:
A warrior protected
by a shell
that can even
deflect the heat
of burning flames.

Name: Mystical Capture Chain
Description:
A mystical chain
that is believed
capable of binding
its enemies and
preventing their
attacks.

Name: Fiend's Hand
Description:
Long arms reach out
from the Swamp
of Chaos to drag
in enemy creatures.

Name: Witty Phantom
Description:
Dressed in a
night-black tuxedo,
this creature
presides over
the doomed.

Name: Mystery Hand
Description:
Twisting the fabric
of reality, arms
stretch out from
another dimension
to attack opponents.

Name: Dragon Statue
Description:
A granite warrior
with a dragon's soul
wields a powerful
sword against
all enemies.

Name: Blue-eyed Silver Zombie
Description:
A creature rumored
to turn enemies
into zombies
with a strange ray
that emanates
from its eyes.

Name: Toad Master
Description:
Thousands of years
old, this frog
wizard attacks
enemies with an
army of tadpoles.

Name: Spiked Snail
Description:
Evolving from the
powers of darkness,
this snail has arms
and legs that allow
swift attacks
against its enemies.

Name: Flame Manipulator
Description:
Attacks enemies with
fire-related spells,
such as the
"Sea of Flames"
and the
"Wall of Fire".

Name: Necrolancer the Timelord
Description:
The first in a line
of golems that
appears almost
anywhere from within
a dimensional ring.

Name: Djinn the Watcher of the Wind
Description:
Controls the air
currents to create
violent winds and
tornadoes to blow
away its enemies.

Name: The Bewitching Phantom Thief
Description:
A flashy,
black-caped thief
who wields
a magic cane.

Name: Temple of Skulls
Description:
A weird temple
of skulls and bones
that sucks the
living essence
of all those who
dare approach it.

Name: Monster Egg
Description:
A warrior hidden
within an egg that
attacks enemies by
flinging eggshells.

Name: The Shadow Who Controls the Dark
Description:
A living shadow
that dwells in the
realm of darkness.
It paralyzes
its enemies
to prevent attacks.

Name: Lord of the Lamp
Description:
A giant that appears
from a mystic lamp
and follows
the orders
of the lamp's owner.

Name: Akihiron
Description:
A mysterious
creature that dwells
below the sea.

Name: Rhaimundos of the Red Sword
Description:
A warrior armed
with the Sword
of Crimson Flames.
Uses fire to bind
the movement
of its enemies.

Name: The Melting Red Shadow
Description:
A creature that
melts into the earth,
melds with an
opponent's shadow,
and attacks
from below.

Name: Dokuroizo the Grim Reaper
Description:
A living spirit that
preys on the living
essence of enemies.

Name: Fire Reaper
Description:
A creature that
deals out punishment
with its
flaming arrows.

Name: Larvas
Description:
A fast-moving,
bird-like creature
that strangles an
opposing monster
with its long,
thin arms.

Name: Hard Armor
Description:
A living suit of
armor that attacks
enemies with a
bone-jarring tackle.

Name: Firegrass
Description:
A fire-breathing
plant found growing
near volcanoes.

Name: Man Eater
Description:
Man-eating plant
with poison feelers
for attacking
enemies.

Name: Dig Beak
Description:
Coiling its
serpent-like body,
this creature spins
and attacks with
its snapping beak.

Name: M-warrior #1
Description:
Specializing in
combination attacks,
this warrior uses
magnetism to block
an enemy's escape.

Name: M-warrior #2
Description:
Specializing in
combination attacks,
this warrior is
equipped with a
tough, magnetically
coated armor.

Name: Tainted Wisdom
Description:
A parasite brain
that preys
on the knowledge
and intelligence
of its opponents.

Name: Lisark
Description:
An unusual creature
with sapphire eyes
that creates visions
to confuse the enemy.

Name: Lord of Zemia
Description:
A vile entity that
deceives enemies
into walking a path
of destruction.

Name: The Judgement Hand
Description:
The hand of final
judgment is capable
of intense attacks
against the enemy.

Name: Mysterious Puppeteer
Description:
A puppet master that
manipulates enemies
during battle.

Name: Ancient Jar
Description:
A fragile jar from
the past containing
a mysterious
creature.

Name: Darkfire Dragon
Description:
Scorching flames
that wipe out
enemies in the blink
of an eye.

Name: Dark King of the Abyss
Description:
King of the
netherworld. It's
said that he once
had the power to
rule over the Dark.

Name: Spirit of the Harp
Description:
A spirit that
soothes the soul
with the music of
its glorious harp.

Name: Big Eye
Description:
This creature is
covered with
hypnotic eyes
for mesmerizing
its enemies.

Name: Armaill
Description:
A strange warrior
who manipulates
three fearsome
blades with
both hands and
its tail.

Name: Dark Prisoner
Description:
This creature
manipulates light
to eliminate
all traces of
its appearance.

Name: Hurricail
Description:
A twister
that runs rampant
in the wastelands,
cutting its enemies
with blades of wind.

Name: Ancient Brain
Description:
Exiled from reality,
this creature is
adept at fighting
in the dark.

Name: Fire Eye
Description:
A winged eye
enveloped in flames
that attacks enemies
with fire.

Name: Monsturtle
Description:
A vicious turtle
with a spiked shell.

Name: Claw Reacher
Description:
Stretching arms and
razor-sharp claws
make this monster a
formidable opponent.

Name: Phantom Dewan
Description:
A wizard
that freezes an
enemy's movement 
with a single curse.

Name: Arlownay
Description:
A maiden
in the flower
blossoms spreads
poisonous pollen
against opponents.

Name: Dark Shade
Description:
Emits a dazzling
light from its
crystal to blind
its enemies.

Name: Masked Clown
Description:
A dancing warrior
that makes mincemeat
out of opponents
with a sharp scythe.

Name: Lucky Trinket
Description:
A thin and reedy
creature protected
by sacred power.

Name: Genin
Description:
Uses amazing
sleight-of-hand
to fool and destroy
its enemies.

Name: Eyearmor
Description:
This warrior
confuses and
destroys enemies
by adopting
their images.

Name: Fiend Refrection #2
Description:
A bird-beast
that summons
reinforcements
with a hand mirror.

Name: Gate Deeg
Description:
A creature
with an abdominal
portal used for
summoning monsters
from the netherworld.

Name: Synchar
Description:
An ugly creature
with two heads and a
mouth for blasting
laser beams.

Name: Fusionist
Description:
A monstrous cat with
wings and a long,
striking tail.

Name: Akakieisu
Description:
A wizard
whose incantations
numb the senses of
opposing monsters.

Name: LaLa Li-oon
Description:
Protected by thunder,
this dangerous cloud
attacks its enemies
with acid rain.

Name: Key Mace
Description:
A small angel
whose cuteness
melts the hearts
of its enemies.

Name: Turtle Tiger
Description:
A tiger encased in a
protective shell
that attacks its
enemies with its
razor-sharp fangs.

Name: Terra the Terrible
Description:
Know as a dweller
of the swamps,
this creature is a
minion of the Dark
forces.

Name: Doron
Description:
An unpredictable
creature that splits
into two and attacks
an enemy from
opposite directions.

Name: Arma Knight
Description:
An ammonite warrior
that has protected
the seas from the
dawn of time.

Name: Mech Mole Zombie
Description:
A creature of the
night that attacks
enemies with its 
rocket-powered arms.

Name: Happy Lover
Description:
A little angel
that fires beams
of happiness
from the heart jewel
on its forehead.

Name: Penguin Knight
Description:
A penguin-like
creature that slides
on its belly
to deliver a blow
with its
outstretched sword.

Name: Petit Dragon
Description:
A very small dragon
known for its
vicious attacks.

Name: Frenzied Panda
Description:
A savage beast
that carries
a big bamboo stick
for beating down
its enemies.

Name: Air Marmot of Nefariousness
Description:
A horned beaver
with wings that
throws high-velocity
acorns from the
sky with uncanny
accuracy.

Name: Phantom Ghost
Description:
Malicious spirits
that walk the world
of the living,
unable to find their
final resting place.

Name: Mabarrel
Description:
A cannon-like
monster that rapidly
fires eyeballs
at the enemy.

Name: Dorover
Description:
An ugly, melting
creature that
breathes out
poison gas.

Name: Twin Long Rods #1
Description:
This creature swings
its whip-like arms
for mid-range
attacks against
enemies.

Name: Droll Bird
Description:
With a battle cry
that curdles
the blood of
its opponent,
this creature
attacks with its
massive beak.

Name: Petit Angel
Description:
A quick-moving and
tiny angel that's
very difficult
to hit.

Name: Winged Cleaver
Description:
This creature
attacks by swinging
around its
sickle-like arms.

Name: Hinotama Soul
Description:
An intensely hot
flame creature that
rams anything that
stands in its way.

Name: Kaminarikozou
Description:
This creature stores
lightning within its
body to deliver
electrifying attacks.

Name: Meotoko
Description:
A huge monster with
a single eye that
fires an intence
beam.

Name: Aqua Madoor
Description:
A wizard of the
waters that conjures
a liquid wall to
crush any enemies
that oppose him.

Name: Kagemusha of the Blue Flame
Description:
Serves as a double
for the ruler of the
Blue Flame. A master
swordsman that
wields a fine blade.

Name: Flame Ghost
Description:
A fiery spirit
that burns anything
in its path.

Name: Dryad
Description:
A spirit of the
forest protected by
the surrounding
plant life.

Name: B. Skull Dragon
Description:
A very rare creature
created from the
fusion of an
uncommon beast and
a vicious dragon.

Name: Two-mouth Darkruler
Description:
A dinosaur with two
crushing jaws.
Stores electricity
in its horn and
releases high
voltage bolts
from the mouth
on its back.

Name: Solitude
Description:
A beast-warrior that
swings a massive
scythe that draws on
the spirit of its
enemies to deliver
devastating blows.

Name: Masked Sorcerer
Description:
A mysterious wizard
whose face remains
forever hidden
behind a strange
mask.

Name: Kumootoko
Description:
A massive,
intelligent spider
that traps its
enemies with webbing.

Name: Midnight Fiend
Description:
A winged creature
rumored to appear
at midnight.

Name: Roaring Ocean Snake
Description:
A massive
sea serpent that
creates tidal waves
to wipe out
its enemies.

Name: Trap Master
Description:
A warrior that
excels in laying
traps such as a
bottomless pit, for
eternally ensnaring
opponents.

Name: Fiend Sword
Description:
Few have escaped
the curse of this
creature. Those that
have done so have
gained untold power.

Name: Skull Stalker
Description:
Swift and vicious,
this monster grabs
its victim with its
pincers and attacks
the captive with its
poison stinger.

Name: Hitodenchak
Description:
A vicious starfish
that spits acid
to melt away
its enemies.

Name: Wood Remains
Description:
A zombie that rose
from the remains of
the woodland ruler.

Name: Hourglass of Life
Description:
A creature
that allows power
to be gained
at the cost of life.

Name: Rare Fish
Description:
An unusual and
ferocious fish with
the head of a beast.

Name: Wood Clown
Description:
An unpleasantly
smiling creature
that wields a scythe
to avoid enemy blows.

Name: Madjinn Gunn
Description:
A living weapon that
fires projectiles
from its mouth.

Name: Dark Titan of Terror
Description:
A spirit said to
dwell in the world
of dreams.
Attacks enemies
in their sleep.

Name: Beautiful Headhuntress
Description:
A lovely swordmaster
with some very
agile moves.

Name: Wodan the Resident of the Forest
Description:
A warrior that has
long resided in the
forest and enjoys
the protection
of Mother Nature.

Name: Guardian of the Labyrinth
Description:
A warrior that
guards the entrance
to the netherworld.

Name: Haniwa
Description:
An earthen doll
that protects
the treasure
in the tombs
of ancient kings.

Name: Yashinoki
Description:
A palm tree with a
will of its own that
attacks enemies by
flinging coconuts.

Name: Vishwar Randi
Description:
A woman warrior that
serves the forces
of darkness.

Name: The Drdek
Description:
An eyeball creature
with legs for
jumping high and
delivering finishing
blows with its sharp
claws.

Name: Dark Assailant
Description:
Armed with Psycho
Sword, this sinister
cutthroat rules the
outer land.

Name: Candle of Fate
Description:
An opponent's fate
is decided
when the flames
of each finger
are extinguished.

Name: Water Element
Description:
A water spirit
that envelops
its opponent
in a thick fog
to cover its attack.

Name: Dissolverock
Description:
A monster borne from
the lava pits.
Generates intensive
heat that can melt
away its enemies.

Name: Meda Bat
Description:
An eyeball fiend
created by a servant
of darkness.
Uses "Dark Spheres"
to blow away
its enemies.

Name: One Who Hunts Souls
Description:
A creature
with a sword
that gains its power
from the life forces
of its victims.

Name: Root Water
Description:
An amphibian capable
of calling up a
massive tidal wave
from the dark seas
to wipe out enemy
monsters.

Name: Master & Expert
Description:
A fearsome duo
consisting of a
beast master and
its loyal servant.

Name: Water Omotics
Description:
Transforms the water
overflowing from a
jar into attacking
dragons.

Name: Hyo
Description:
An ice warrior whose
slightest touch
freezes an opponent.

Name: Enchanting Mermaid
Description:
A beautiful mermaid
that lures voyagers
to a watery grave.

Name: Nekogal #1
Description:
A cat creature that
looks cute to the
eye but delivers
scratching blows
with its sharp claws.

Name: Angelwitch
Description:
A creature
that chose the
path of sorcery
to become a witch.

Name: Embryonic Beast
Description:
A repulsive monster
with a gaping belly
that swallows almost
anything.

Name: Prevent Rat
Description:
This monster is
shielded by 
a hide covered
in thick hair.

Name: Dimensional Warrior
Description:
A monster
capable of creating
dimensional rifts
to trap its enemies.

Name: Stone Armadiller
Description:
With a body armored
by rock-hard fur,
this monster
features excellent
defense capabilities.

Name: Beastking of the Swamps
Description:
This creature
changes the ground
at its feet into
quicksand to ensnare
its enemies.

Name: Ancient Sorcerer
Description:
A master fighter
that uses various
staffs to render
enemies unconscious.

Name: Lunar Queen Elzaim
Description:
A lovely
moon goddess that
can throw up
a lunar curtain
to block
enemy attacks.

Name: Wicked Mirror
Description:
A malevolent mirror
that hypnotizes
a beholder and
renders the victim
susceptible
to attacks.

Name: The Little Swordsman of Aile
Description:
An elf warrior
mounted on a huge
lizard.

Name: Rock Ogre Grotto #2
Description:
A stone golem
that turns opponents
into rocks and
crushes them to dust.

Name: Wing Egg Elf
Description:
Hiding within its
eggshell, this
creature blocks
enemy attacks with
its massive wings.

Name: The Furious Sea King
Description:
Grand King of the
Seven Seas.
Able to summon
massive tidal waves
to drown the enemy.

Name: Princess of Tsurugi
Description:
A queen of swords
that is virtually
unequalled in her
mastery of every
blade imaginable
to man.

Name: Unknown Warrior of Fiend
Description:
The speed of this
warrior creates
an intense vacuum
that can actually
slice through
a monster's hide.

Name: Sectarian of Secrets
Description:
A sorcerer that
worships the dark
forces and can
summon a massive
hand to drag away
opponents into
the netherworld.

Name: Versago the Destroyer
Description:
A lord of
destruction
born from the heart
of darkness,
this creature
can summon storms
to destroy opponents.

Name: Wetha
Description:
A rain spirit that
can summon typhoons
to blow away its
enemies.

Name: Megirus Light
Description:
This creature's
ominous eyes can
unleash piercing
rays against its
enemies.

Name: Mavelus
Description:
Related to the
phoenix, this
creature dwells in
the mountains. Its
fiery breath is
extremely scorching.

Name: Ancient Tree of Enlightenment
Description:
Armed with a wealth
of knowledge, this
monster is able to
block just about
any attack.

Name: Green Phantom King
Description:
This youthful king
of the forests lives
in a green world,
abundant with trees
and wildlife.

Name: Ground Attacker Bugroth
Description:
A land-based armored
robot that is said
to once have marine
attack capabilities.

Name: Ray & Temperature
Description:
The Sun and the
North Wind join
hands to deliver
a devastating
combination of heat
and gale-force winds.

Name: Gorgon Egg
Description:
A gorgon's egg with
eyes said to create
whatever creature
crosses its view.

Name: Petit Moth
Description:
Nobody has any idea
what creature may
spawn from this
mysterious larva.

Name: King Fog
Description:
A spectre that
dwells in a blinding
curtain of smoke.

Name: Protector of the Throne
Description:
A creature that
protects the king's
throne from usurpers.

Name: Mystic Clown
Description:
Nothing can stop the
mad attack of this
powerful creature.

Name: Mystical Sheep #2
Description:
A monstrous sheep
with a long tail for
hypnotizing enemies
to render them
powerless.

Name: Holograh
Description:
A monster machine
that generates
images to confuse
its enemies,
making them prone
to attacks.

Name: Tao the Chanter
Description:
A magic-user that
corrodes the yin
and yang to create
a twisted power
to attack enemies.

Name: Serpent Marauder
Description:
A snake with a
single eye that
blows an icy breath
to freeze its
opponents.

Name: Gatekeeper
Description:
An indestructible
machine
built to protect
key entrances.

Name: Ogre of the Black Shadow
Description:
An ogre possessed
by the powers
of the dark.
Few can withstand
its rapid charge.

Name: Dark Artist
Description:
A demented artist
that creates
objets d'art
to crush enemies.

Name: Change Slime
Description:
A shape-shifting
slime that is
capable of adopting
the form of other
creatures.

Name: Moon Envoy
Description:
A servant of the
moon goddess,
this warrior
wields a pike
with a spectacular
crescent-shaped
blade.

Name: Fireyarou
Description:
A malevolent
creature
wrapped in flames
that attacks enemies
with intense fire.

Name: Psychic Kappa
Description:
An amphibian with
extrasensory powers
for blocking attacks.

Name: Masaki the Legendary Swordsman
Description:
Legendary
swordmaster and a
veteran of over 100
battles.

Name: Dragoness the Wicked Knight
Description:
A warrior
equipped with
equipment fashioned
from dragon scales.

Name: Bio Plant
Description:
A monstrous creature
born from a failed
lab experiment.

Name: One-eyed Shield Dragon
Description:
This dragon wears a
shield not only for
its own protection
but also for ramming
its enemies.

Name: Cyber Soldier of Darkworld
Description:
An unstoppable
mechanical soldier
powered by dark
forces.

Name: Wicked Dragon with the Ersatz Head
Description:
A two-headed dragon
with a pair of
vicious jaws for
crushing its enemies.

Name: Sonic Maid
Description:
A maiden
that uses sound
to her advantage.
She wields a scythe
that's shaped
like a musical note.

Name: Kurama
Description:
A vicious bird that
attacks from the
skies with its
whip-like tail.

Name: Legendary Sword
Description:
A sword that brings
out the best in
warriors. It cannot
be used by servants
of the dark.

Name: Sword of Dark Destruction
Description:
Dark forces
increase the power
of Warriors!

Name: Dark Energy
Description:
Dark forces increase
the power of Fiends
and other monsters
of the Dark!

Name: Axe of Despair
Description:
Fiends and
Beast-Warriors can
constantly use their
maximum strength!

Name: Laser Cannon Armor
Description:
Arms Insects with
a powerful laser!

Name: Insect Armor with Laser Cannon
Description:
Allows Insects to
fire an intense
blast of fire!

Name: Elf's Light
Description:
Increases the power
of elves with
mystical light!

Name: Beast Fangs
Description:
Increases the power
of Beasts and other
fanged monsters!

Name: Steel Shell
Description:
Boosts the power of
shelled monsters!
Said to have no
effect on those
without shells.

Name: Vile Germs
Description:
Vile microbes boost
the power of Plants
in the woods!

Name: Black Pendant
Description:
This pendant grants
extra power
to Dark sorcerers!

Name: Silver Bow and Arrow
Description:
Silver bow and arrow
enhances the power
of Fairies.

Name: Horn of Light
Description:
Increases the power
of horned creatures!
Has no effect
on Dark monsters.

Name: Horn of the Unicorn
Description:
Increases the power
of Dark monsters
with horns!

Name: Dragon Treasure
Description:
A legendary treasure
that increases the
power of dragons.

Name: Electro-whip
Description:
A whip for
paralyzing enemies.
Increases power when
equipped with
female creatures.

Name: Cyber Shield
Description:
Increases the power
of female monsters
by changing their
attitudes.

Name: Elegant Egotist
Description:
Creates two
doppelgangers of
Harpy Lady for
three-pronged
attacks!

Name: Mystical Moon
Description:
Moonlight increases
the power of Beasts!

Name: Stop Defense
Description:
Forces an opponent's
monster card
positioned for
defense into the
attack position.

Name: Malevolent Nuzzler
Description:
Diabolic forces act
to increase the
power of female and
Dark monsters!

Name: Violet Crystal
Description:
Mystic forces from
the crystal increase
the power of Zombies.

Name: Book of Secret Arts
Description:
A magic book for
increasing the power
of magic-users.
It cannot be used
by bad-hearted
sorcerers.

Name: Invigoration
Description:
Increases the power
of Thunder, Rock,
and Pyro monsters.

Name: Machine Conversion Factory
Description:
A manufacturing
facility that tunes
up all Machine
monsters.

Name: Raise Body Heat
Description:
Absorbs the sun's
energy to increase
the power of
Dinosaurs!

Name: Follow Wind
Description:
The winds provide
support to increase
the power of Winged
Beasts and other
flying monsters!

Name: Power of Kaishin
Description:
Poseidon's Strength
is shared to boost
the power of
Aqua, Fish, and
Sea Serpent
monsters!

Name: Dragon Capture Jar
Description:
Destroys
all opponent
Dragon monsters
on the playfield!

Name: Forest
Description:
Changes the field
in favor of
Beast-Warrior,
Insect, Plant, and
Beast monsters!

Name: Wasteland
Description:
Changes the field
in favor of Zombie,
Dinosaur and
Rock monsters!

Name: Mountain
Description:
Changes the field
in favor of Dragon,
Winged Beast, and
Thunder monsters!

Name: Sogen
Description:
Changes the field
to meadow land
in favor of Warrior
and Beast-Warrior
monsters!

Name: Umi
Description:
Changes the field
in favor of Aqua
and Thunder monsters,
but unfavorable to
Machine and Pyro
monsters!

Name: Yami
Description:
Changes the field
in favor of
Magic-User and
Fiend monsters,
but unfavorable
to Fairy monsters!

Name: Dark Hole
Description:
Sucks up every card
in play on the field!

Name: Raigeki
Description:
Destroys every
opposing monster
with a stroke
of lightning!

Name: Mooyan Curry
Description:
A delicious
beef curry increases
Life Points by 200!

Name: Red Medicine
Description:
A magic potion
that increases
Life Points by 500!

Name: Goblin's Secret Remedy
Description:
A goblin's herb
that increases
Life Points by 1000!

Name: Soul of the Pure
Description:
A fairy potion
that increases
Life Points by 2000!

Name: Dian Keto the Cure Master
Description:
A mystical power
that increases
Life Points by 5000!

Name: Sparks
Description:
A shower of sparks
inflicts 50 points
of damage
to your opponent's
Life Points!!

Name: Hinotama
Description:
A fireball
inflicts 100 points
of damage
to your opponent's
Life Points!!

Name: Final Flame
Description:
Flames
inflict 200 points
of damage
to your opponent's
Life Points!!

Name: Ookazi
Description:
Flames
inflict 500 points
of damage
to your opponent's
Life Points!

Name: Tremendous Fire
Description:
An inferno
inflicts 1000 points
of damage
to your opponent's
Life Points!

Name: Swords of Revealing Light
Description:
Enemy monsters
are revealed and
your opponent
cannot attack
for three turns.

Name: Spellbinding Circle
Description:
A curse reduces the
power of all enemy
monsters!

Name: Dark-piercing Light
Description:
A dazzling light
reveals all monsters
on the playing field.

Name: Yaranzo
Description:
A monster that
attacks anybody
who attempts
to open its lid.

Name: Kanan the Swordmistress
Description:
A lady swordsman
that floats like a
butterfly and stings
like a bee.

Name: Takriminos
Description:
A finned creature
distantly related
to sea Dragons.

Name: Stuffed Animal
Description:
A deceptively cute
stuffed animal that
bites.

Name: Megasonic Eye
Description:
A cryptic doomsday
machine that comes
from the edge of
the universe.

Name: Super War-lion
Description:
A very vicious lion
with sharp and
long claws.

Name: Yamadron
Description:
A three-headed,
fire-breathing
monster.

Name: Seiyaryu
Description:
A sacred dragon
that burns away
wickedness with its
mystical flames.

Name: Three-legged Zombies
Description:
Bony and Tubby,
a friendly pair
of skeletons.

Name: Zera The Mant
Description:
A huge, brutal
monster that attacks
with razor-sharp
claws.

Name: Flying Penguin
Description:
A rare penguin that
flies with the wings
on its head.

Name: Millennium Shield
Description:
A Millennium Item
candidate
that is said
to block any
powerful attack.

Name: Fairy's Gift
Description:
Flies around
spreading happiness
to all.

Name: Black Luster Soldier
Description:
A powerful warrior
with the same
capabilities as the
legendary Blue-eyes
White Dragon.

Name: Fiend's Mirror
Description:
An arcane glass
that draws
its enemies into
the mirror world.

Name: Labyrinth Wall
Description:
Walls appear
on the field to form
a labyrinth with
no exit.

Name: Jirai Gumo
Description:
A monster spider
that dwells
under the earth.

Name: Shadow Ghoul
Description:
A dangerous zombie
that crawls
in the dark.

Name: Wall Shadow
Description:
An unusually fast
monster that sweeps
across walls to
attack its enemies.

Name: Labyrinth Tank
Description:
A tank that races
around a labyrinth
hunting down
its enemies.

Name: Sanga of the Thunder
Description:
A golem that uses
lightning attacks
similar to the
Labyrinth Brothers.

Name: Kazejin
Description:
A golem that
controls the winds
like the Labyrinth
Brothers.

Name: Suijin
Description:
A golem that uses
water attacks like
the Labyrinth
Brothers.

Name: Gate Guardian
Description:
Sanga, Kazejin, and
Suijin join to
form a single,
powerful monster.

Name: Dungeon Worm
Description:
Hidden under
the floors of
a labyrinth,
it swallows any
who pass above.

Name: Monster Tamer
Description:
A master of monsters
that exercises
control over several
creatures.

Name: Ryu-kishin Powered
Description:
Ryu-kishin enhanced
by the powers of
darkness. Very sharp
talons make it
a worthy opponent.

Name: Swordstalker
Description:
A monster formed by
the vengeful souls
of those who passed
away in battle.

Name: La Jinn the Mystical Genie
Description:
A genie of the lamp
that's at the beck
and call of its
master.

Name: Blue-eyes Ultimate Dragon
Description:
The ultimate dragon
formed by the fusion
of three Blue-eyes
White Dragons.

Name: Toon Alligator
Description:
An alligator monster
straight from
the cartoons.

Name: Rude Kaiser
Description:
With an axe in each
hand, this monster
delivers heavy
damage.

Name: Parrot Dragon
Description:
A dragon from the
cartoons that's more
dangerous than it
appears to be.

Name: Dark Rabbit
Description:
A cartoon rabbit
that quickly leaps
all over the place,
making it a
difficult target.

Name: Bickuribox
Description:
A jack-in-the-box
that excels
in surprise attacks.

Name: Harpie's Pet Dragon
Description:
A favorite pet for
harpies, but a very
dangerous dragon.

Name: Mystic Lamp
Description:
A lamp
used by wizards
to mix potions.

Name: Pendulum Machine
Description:
A horrible torture
machine with a large
pendulum blade.

Name: Giltia the D. Knight
Description:
Armed with a
soul-searing spear,
this creature favors
magic attacks.

Name: Launcher Spider
Description:
A spider machine
that launches
explosive rockets
against its enemies.

Name: Zoa
Description:
A monster
whose full potential
can be achieved
when transformed
into its metal form.

Name: Metalzoa
Description:
A metallic Zoa
capable of
intensive attacks.

Name: Zone Eater
Description:
A sea creature that
swallows enemies and
slowly digests them.

Name: Steel Scorpion
Description:
An iron-tailed
monster equipped
with very sharp
scissors.

Name: Dancing Elf
Description:
An elf that dances
across the sky with
wings of razor-sharp
blades.

Name: Ocubeam
Description:
Frightening in
appearance, this
creature uses its
large eyes and ears
to keep track
of any movement.

Name: Leghul
Description:
Not a very powerful
monster despite its
large fangs and
spikes.

Name: Ooguchi
Description:
A monstrous bullfrog
with poison spikes.

Name: Swordsman from a Foreign Land
Description:
An eastern warrior
armed with a cursed
sword.

Name: Emperor of the Land and Sea
Description:
A fire-breathing
reptilian monster.

Name: Ushi Oni
Description:
A bull monster
resurrected by
the dark arts
that appears
from inside a jar.

Name: Monster Eye
Description:
A servant that
maintains a close
watch on anything
and everything.
It throws up
a smokescreen
when discovered.

Name: Leogun
Description:
Huge monster
with a lion's mane
similar to the
"King of Beasts".

Name: Tatsunootoshigo
Description:
A fast-moving sea
monster that has the
bodies of a horse
and a fish.

Name: Saber Slasher
Description:
A rampaging machine
that wields
a massive sword.

Name: Yaiba Robo
Description:
A machine
with several blades
hidden within
its square body.

Name: Machine King
Description:
Armored with super
alloy, this robot
attacks with blasts
of fire launched
from both arms.

Name: Giant Mech-soldier
Description:
This monster swings
an earth-shaking axe
that can eliminate
enemies with
a single blow.

Name: Metal Dragon
Description:
A golden,
fire-breathing
dragon that burns
any opponent
in its path.

Name: Mechanical Spider
Description:
A spider-shaped,
mechanized monster
with sickles at
the end of its legs.

Name: Bat
Description:
A mechanized bat
that attacks
by dropping
explosion orbs.

Name: Giga-tech Wolf
Description:
A wolf made entirely
of iron. Its steel
jaws can bite
through anything.

Name: Cyber Soldier
Description:
Round-shaped
soldiers that roll
around and act as
guardians to the
Machine King.

Name: Shovel Crusher
Description:
Armed with
a pair of shovels,
this creature is
a walking engine
of destruction.

Name: Mechanicalchacer
Description:
A hunter that
relentlessly pursues
its target by order
of the Machine King.

Name: Blocker
Description:
Each separate part
of this creature is
an individual weapon
capable of
devastating attacks.

Name: Blast Juggler
Description:
A walking time
device that loves
to blow enemies
away.

Name: Golgoil
Description:
A massive iron golem
that appears from
a dimensional rift.

Name: Giganto
Description:
This creature swings
around a huge spiked
ball to destroy its
enemies.

Name: Cyber-Stein
Description:
Created in a
basement lab, this
infernal machine
launches rockets
from within its
mouth.

Name: Cyber Commander
Description:
A strike force
equipped with
rader detectors
and sensors.

Name: Jinzo #7
Description:
Created in an
underground lab,
this artificial
being occasionally
goes berserk.

Name: Dice Armadillo
Description:
An armadillo-like
creature that forms
a die whenever it
rolls up its body.

Name: Sky Dragon
Description:
A bird-like dragon
with four bladed
wings.

Name: Thunder Dragon
Description:
A dragon that
summons thunder and
lightning to attack
its opponents.

Name: Stone D.
Description:
With a body
